headline: Jet Aviation Redelivers Two Modified Bell 429 Helicopters to Middle East Customer
summary: BASEL, Switzerland - Jet Aviation announced today that it has redelivered two Bell 429 helicopters to a customer in the Middle East. The aircraft were the final two in a total fleet of six modified...
